<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
 <nav style="text-align: center; padding: 15px; background: #17458F;">
  <a href="index.html" style="color: white; margin: 0 15px; text-decoration: none; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Home</a>
  <a href="Communications Hub.html" style="color: white; margin: 0 15px; text-decoration: none; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Communications Hub</a>
